Class SongGroup

java.lang.Object

java.lang.Comparable
public class SongGroup
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable

A songgroup is typically a group of songs of the same genre, for every directory in the repository directory we make a new songgroup named after the directory.
